summary.span: 为 SourceChanged 事件提供用于互操作的数据。

span.span: Provides data for the SourceChanged event, used for interoperation.
This class cannot be inherited.

remarks.format: ## Remarks SourceChanged 事件是一个路由事件, 其中事件标识符不公开公开。The SourceChanged event is a routed event where the event identifier is not publicly exposed. 这是因为此事件在互操作中扮演着潜在的关键部分, 不应允许任何其他源 (而不是已知子类的内部实现) 随意引发此事件 (目前只有这样的类是).This is because this event plays a potentially critical part in interoperation and should not be allowed to be raised arbitrarily by any other source than the internal implementation of a known subclass (currently, the only such class is ). 实现互操作解决方案时, 可以附加或移除事件的处理程序 (分别调用和), 但不能执行通常可用于路由事件 (例如类处理) 的其他操作。添加所有者, 或从任意元素源引发事件。When implementing an interoperation solution, you can attach or remove handlers for the event (by calling and , respectively) but you cannot perform other operations normally available to routed events such as class handling, adding owners, or raising the event from an arbitrary element source. 此类将重写虚拟方法, 以便在事件系统请求时返回特定于类型的处理程序。This class overrides the virtual method , in order to return a type-specific handler when requested by the event system. 此替代不会显示在本[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_sdk](~/includes/tla2sharptla-sdk-md.md)]文档的类成员表中, 因为它是由密封类实现的受保护成员。 This override does not appear in the class members table in this [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_sdk](~/includes/tla2sharptla-sdk-md.md)] documentation because it is a protected member implemented by a sealed class.
